{"type": "article", "id": 24075, "title": "吊床和摇椅", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-18T07:00:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 62, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135453FWMIGoz3nXl5r4KJ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是由 3 位来自印度浦那的学生设计的椅子，她们将摇椅和吊床结合起来，用了黑铁结构和不同的编织方式，在椅子下面增加了弧形的支撑，使它可以摇晃。椅子的结构是圆形的，像一个月亮门。它其实用了两根黑铁框，窄的一边是可提椅子的扶手，而宽的一边是座位。3 位学生想在两周内完成一把椅子，而这把椅子也有巧妙和聪明的地方。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135450BYnGZwJPitpebf9k.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135451iA0xGIUFMh3VXONj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.40375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021354519oQ7WP1wsMNpBuIy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.09625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135452QHxWuhX9DzVOpL7A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135452YL58q2U64fTyIRJs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.36625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}